@node Region marking action
@section Region marking action

@findex avy-extras-action-mark-to-char
The function @code{avy-extras-action-mark-to-char} is an avy action function that activates the mark and moves point to the selected position, effectively creating a region from the original point to the avy target. This is useful as a custom avy action for selecting text between two positions.

This function is adapted from Karthink's ``Avy can do anything'' guide.

